Subject: Re: PRO/AH> E. coli: superbug or mere sensation? (02)
With carriage rates for EHEC of up to 50% reported all antibiotics would do
is create antibiotic resisitant EHEC. Do we want this?
It is not just E. coli O157, it is all the other toxigenic E.coli carried
that matter.
